Name: It's My Party, I Can Cry If I Want To
Description: If you've cried to it (or about it), submit it and we'll vote on them.

Name: Bloodsucker Ballads
Description: It's about vampires, so please show us your best song about vampires. Either figuratively or literally but in some way, shape, or form. About vampires.

Name: Unheard Of
Description:
This week is:
A song from a small artist you love, something you absolutely want to introduce people to.

(Aim for bands with low listeners, local folks you like, people with pretty generally "unheard of" stuff.)

Name: Familiar Places
Description:
This round is about:
SONGS WITH THE NAME OF A LOCATION IN THE TITLE

Like Monterrey, Circle K, Calabasas, or Twin Peaks.

Name: 101 Songs To Improve Your Mood
Description: Songs you put on to improve your mood, songs that you need to make a bad day good and maybe even terrible ones just a little better.
